  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745220/extras/6227fbe155c5bba0d65718a6a894834f.avif?t=1662668227\" width=610 height=130 /></span><br>Mr. DomusMundi is the prince who decides the fate of the kingdom. You have only two possible solutions, each option leads to certain consequences. <br>Prince Mundi solves only global issues on the scale of the kingdom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745220/extras/79243d5a5b13c73c705a0129158e2ad8.poster.avif?t=1662668227\" width=610 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745220/extras/79243d5a5b13c73c705a0129158e2ad8.webm?t=1662668227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1745220/extras/79243d5a5b13c73c705a0129158e2ad8.mp4?t=1662668227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Several options for passing the game;<br></li><li>The irreversible consequences of the choice force the player to make difficult decisions;  <br></li><li>A choice with consequences and a game with platformer elements.<br></li><li>War or scientific progress, or a loan at high-interest rates, it's up to you to decide what will happen to the kingdom.</li></ul>",
